creator: Treble LLC
descriptionHtml:
App Descriptions

Treble® is reinventing business networking. Treble helps you unlock hidden business and career opportunities within your trusted business network by making it easy to efficiently engage, nurture and, most importantly, leverage your business relationships. Think of Treble as a “CRM for your business network” rather than just another social media/marketing platform.
Treble helps you make and receive referrals and introductions, track who and which organizations are most beneficial for you and proactively suggest valuable actions you can take to generate goodwill within your network so you can tap into it when you need assistance. Better still, as you hone your networking, you’ll start receiving valuable, inbound referrals from people you actually know.
Make sure you take full advantage of Treble’s “Wish Engine” so your trusted business associates know exactly how to help you and, increase the power of your network by reviewing others’ wishes and helping them. The more you help others, the more goodwill you generate and the more likely others will help you in return. That’s the power of reciprocity. That’s the power of Treble!

What’s New

Thanks for being part of the Treble community!

We are excited to release this new version of Treble – Treble 3.0! In this new version everything got an
update! We redesigned from the ground up! We hope you love it as much as we do.

Here are a few highlights:

- There’s now a streamlined community tab to stay up to date on all important news and events from the amazing organizations you’re a part of. (Be sure to let us know if you’re a part of an organization that’s not on Treble yet – we’re always looking to add more to our community!)

- We’ve also centralized all communication into an inbox. From here you can easily make an intro, give a referral, send a message, say thank you (remember to always say thank you!), and record any interactions you have with your network even if they don’t happen from Treble. (Remember, Treble is a CRM for your network – tracking these interactions is incredibly valuable.)

- And Wishes, the iconic feature of Treble, is still the most powerful way to crowdsource your network for a business “needs/wants or asks” but with a fresh new look.

Be sure to let us know what you think. We love to hear from you! Also, be sure to send us your success stories! We want to hear about the new job you landed via Treble, the newest business transaction or simply a great new connection you made through Treble.

Send the details to Support@TrebleNetwork.com.

Happy Trebling!

Privacy policy:
https://www.treblenetwork.com/privacy-policy/

Terms of use:
https://www.treblenetwork.com/terms
